desc_long								关于这款游戏							In this tug-of-war, casual defense game， you play Leonidas who is the hero-king of Sparta,  against hordes of attacking zombies in Thermopylae. Recruit allies and build defenses to stop them!● Leonidas actually learned magic, very useful, very powerful, very funny.● A wide variety of allies to summon including swordsmen, Royal Guards, archers, witches and more.● More flexible combination of tactics.● Special supply system.● 60 waves in classic mode, and after accomplished difficulty will increase.● 3 kinds of endless mode, wilder, more fun.● Beautiful graphics, epic battle.						
